'''Michael Ralph''' (born [[1960s#1963|1963]]) provided the voice for the [[Steadfast (tank)|Steadfast]] and Torpedo Launcher pilots in ''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]''. He also voiced Rebel Wingman 5 in ''[[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron II: Rogue Leader]]'' and provided additional voiced for ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''.

